kdown of democracy in the Weimar Republic. It is also an engrossing tale of a Communist con man whose name once aroused fear, loathing, and admiration around the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCommunismxHistoryx20th centuryxGermany. 0aCommunismxHistoryx20th centuryxSoviet Union. 0aCommunismzGermanyxHistoryy20th century. 0aCommunismzSoviet UnionxHistoryy20th century. 0aCommunistsxBiographyxGermany. 0aCommunistszGermanyvBiography. 0aPropaganda, CommunistxHistory. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Historical.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030013009640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300130096423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300130096/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles